When Titanic came out I was 18, and I was a student in Iran. At the time I used to dye my hair red (because I have a pale skin) and it is naturally curly , I used to wear reddish lipstick and everybody called me ''Rose''. I don't look like Kate Winslet at all, but I think my looks was trendy at the time because of Titanic. I was so silly I was upset because I thought Rose was fat! I was young and naive. There was a boy in our class with a rather long blonde hair and we got famous in the entire university as ''Jack & Rose''. It was very awkward at the time, but those are my memories.
